					</div>
				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: The Problem With Passion</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-08-26T16:55:01+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">August 26, 2014 12:55 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">August 26, 2014 12:55 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
</button>
		</div>
			</header>
		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/08/26/today-in-small-business-the-problem-with-passion/" data-title="Today in Small Business: The Problem With Passion" data-description="Stanford offers a free online course on how to build a business. Some merchants use Bitcoin A.T.M.s to attract customers. And meet a business owner who loves air travel (even turbulence).">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>The Economy</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="//www.cnbc.com/id/101940801">New home sales slid</a> in July, hitting their lowest level since March.</li>
<li><a href="//247wallst.com/autos/2014/08/25/auto-sales-headed-for-record-setting-august/?">Auto sales</a> are headed for a record-setting August.</li>
<li>Texas <a href="//www.mysanantonio.com/business/local/article/Dallas-Fed-Texas-factory-growth-slows-5711172.php">factory growth</a> slows.</li>
<li><a href="//online.wsj.com/articles/durable-goods-orders-surge-22-6-in-july-1409056584">Durable goods</a> orders surge.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Entrepreneurship</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>What <a href="//www.businessinsider.com/business-lessons-from-boxing-2014-8?">boxing taught</a> one small-business owner about entrepreneurship.</li>
<li>Here is how one <a href="//kotaku.com/how-one-gamer-went-from-addict-to-entrepreneur-1626410573">video gamer</a> went from &#8220;addict&#8221; to entrepreneur.</li>
