<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Management</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A couple of Stanford professors are offering <a href="//www.gsb.stanford.edu/news/headlines/learn-grow-your-business-without-screwing-up-free-online-course">a free online course</a> on how to develop a business.</li>
<li>Here is how <a href="//www.fastcolabs.com/3034792/how-fast-food-chains-pick-their-next-location?partner=rss">fast food chains</a> pick their locations.</li>
<li>Hotels are charging a <a href="//time.com/3173820/hotel-fees/">record amount</a> of fees this year.</li>
<li>Amazon pays almost a billion dollars for a <a href="//venturebeat.com/2014/08/25/amazon-acquires-twitch-worlds-largest-e-tailer-buys-largest-gameplay-livestreaming-site/">gameplay streaming site</a>.</li>
<li>Burger King <a href="//www.businessweek.com/articles/2014-08-25/burger-king-looks-to-ride-coffee-boom-save-on-taxes-by-acquiring-tim-hortons%23r=rss">looks to ride</a> the coffee boom (and maybe save on taxes, too).</li>
<li>Efforts to <a href="//www.leaderpost.com/business/Jell+struggles+turnaround+fails/10146293/story.html">turn around Jell-O</a> have disappointed so far.</li>
<li>A <a href="//online.wsj.com/articles/how-an-entrepreneur-s-passion-can-destroy-a-startup-1408912044?">business owner&#8217;s passion</a> can be far more dangerous than many realize.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Marketing</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Some merchants are <a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/08/25/on-to-do-list-deposit-cash-in-bitcoin-a-t-m/">using Bitcoin A.T.M.s</a> to attract customers.</li>
<li>Not yet profitable, HubSpot, an online marketer for small businesses, <a href="//venturebeat.com/2014/08/25/hubspot-files-to-go-public-with-a-100m-ipo/">files to go public</a>.</li>
