</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Taxes</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The Internal Revenue Serviceâs number of <a href="//www.reuters.com/article/2014/08/25/us-irs-enforcement-budget-idUSKBN0GP0VY20140825?rpc=40">enforcement agents</a> could drop to the lowest levels since the 1970s.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Start-Ups</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Cities across the world are slated to compete in Novemberâs <a href="//www.bizjournals.com/dallas/news/2014/08/25/dfw-entreprenuers-to-compete-in-global-startup.html">Global Startup Battle</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Retailing</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>An industry expert says changes in <a href="//nrn.com/technology/restaurant-operations-watch-disruptions-delivery?">restaurant delivery</a> are coming fast.</li>
<li>Do you think this <a href="//abc13.com/entertainment/hilarious-local-restaurant-ad-so-bad-its-brilliant/277042/">restaurant commercial</a> is âepically awfulâ?</li>
<li>A logistics and transportation expert wonders if <a href="//www.forbes.com/sites/stevebanker/2014/08/25/amazon-grows-rapidly-traditional-retailers-struggle-should-brick-and-mortar-retailers-partner-with-google/">brick-and-mortar retailers</a> should be teaming up with Google.</li>
<li>In San Diego, more than <a href="//online.wsj.com/article/PR-CO-20140825-908333.html">100 regional small businesses</a> get a chance to present their food and beverage products as candidates to be featured in Sam&#8217;s Club stores.</li>
<li>Some <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/business/economy/not-so-cool-anymore-teen-focused-retailers-like-abercrombie-try-to-reinvent-themselves/2014/08/24/789b02b8-29f9-11e4-86ca-6f03cbd15c1a_story.html">teenager-focused retailers</a> like Abercrombie &#038; Fitch are trying to reinvent themselves.</li>
</ul>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Employees</strong></p>
<ul>
